I am a postdoctoral fellow in Plant Sciences at the University of Saskatchewan. I currently lead the metagenomic and bioinformatic components of **[Grassland Genomics for Greenhouse Gas Mitigation](https://grassland-genomics.usask.ca/research-studies) (GG4GHG)**, a Genome Canada–funded program that investigates how plant genetic and species diversity, together with soil microbial and insect communities, shapes carbon storage, greenhouse gas mitigation potential, and other ecosystem services in Canadian grasslands.
:::

